  <description type="morphology">Plants 10–70 cm. Leaves glabrous, scabroso-hirtellous, ± hirsute to hirtellous, or villous, glandular or not, glands yellow. Involucres 2.5–10 mm. Anthers yellow, brownish, or purple. Pappi of 3–5 linear or subulate scales.</description>
  <description type="distribution">California, nw Mexico.</description>
